# Plans and designs embed ```yaml fences copied verbatim from openapi.yaml, whose
# indentation encodes WHERE the snippet goes (e.g. 4-deep under
# components.schemas). Prettier reformats fenced code it recognises and
# de-indents those blocks to column 0, silently destroying that meaning — the
# snippet still looks fine, it just now says something else. prisma/sql fences
# are untouched only because Prettier doesn't parse them.
